# FinalProject - Online Shopping Platform

Welcome to the K & V Online Shopping Platform. This project is a simple e-commerce website that allows users to browse products, add items to their cart, and manage their orders. The project also includes user authentication through traditional login/register methods and OAuth2 using Google and GitHub.

## Features

- User Authentication: 
  - Traditional username/password login and registration.
  - OAuth2 integration for Google and GitHub.
  
- Shopping Cart: 
  - Add items to the cart from the product catalog.
  - Update item quantities or remove items from the cart.
  - View total costs dynamically.

- Responsive Design: 
  - Modern and user-friendly interface.
  - Compatible with multiple devices and screen sizes.

- Backend and API:
  - Node.js and Express.js used for backend development.
  - REST API endpoints for cart management and user authentication.

## API Endpoints

### Authentication
- GET /login: Login page
- GET /register: Registration page
- GET /auth/google: Google OAuth login
- GET /auth/github: GitHub OAuth login
- POST /auth/logout: Logout user

### Cart
- GET /api/cart: Get all cart items and total cost
- POST /api/cart: Add an item to the cart
- PUT /api/cart/:id: Update item quantity
- DELETE /api/cart/:id: Remove an item from the cart

